                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17971025-51-off258 t17971025-51-cd259"></join>, sixteen pair of boys beaver gloves, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17971025-51-victim417" type="victimName">
                  William 
